{"tid":326051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"酒量係點衡量","createTime":"2017-07-17T16:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T16:23:07.000Z","uid":19502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"214f79ea8ceba0587600b70991aeb63b3145e86b","tid":326051,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"有一排成日飲酒<br />\n可以飲到起碼10罐啤酒先覺得有醉意<br />\n但依家飲兩罐1664就已經wingwing地<br />\n都隔咗起碼三個月 真係要keep住飲先酒量好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw依家有啲醉 打錯5p字請原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7089f0757d3e86b31c90e3c82738dfe0d264d4c0","tid":326051,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"其實就算我之前飲到10罐<br />\n但我都覺得自己好渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知點解今晚無啦啦想飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想戒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd2f0ec726a1eaddffe817a1f92a0e2e5e8a675","tid":326051,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:14:01.000Z","msg":"無人喺度咩i我好聚啊我想同人傾吓計呀"},{"pid":"0a5acc2ca1c1dbf37a0d7f02b6e22aa0435d5bc7","tid":326051,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:15:29.000Z","msg":"I依家真係冇人理喎"},{"pid":"c633a3e70c627d02daa17b2954afa07beb017fe5","tid":326051,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"仆街啦我覺得自己聽朝會後悔開你個post羅"},{"pid":"43cf609a6e58eac0a57137e6b2a49ef52b8a1a60","tid":326051,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"飲兩L消毒火酒都唔醉"},{"pid":"3962c9a05120c32aca9ddb0596f28a36e733a37b","tid":326051,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲兩L消毒火酒都唔醉</blockquote><br />\n我飲開滴露"},{"pid":"c46ea1866ffa76985359609cee